    <briefdescription>
<para>The secure storage ITS transform module. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The functions declared in this header implement the ITS transform module. They are meant to be called only by the ITS implementation. This header may be included when providing a custom implementation of the ITS transform module (<computeroutput>CONFIG_SECURE_STORAGE_ITS_TRANSFORM_IMPLEMENTATION_CUSTOM</computeroutput>). </para>
